From: DevBox UML arm64 Port
Subject: [PATCH] arm64: um: add asm/archparam.h stub

arm64 has no LAST_PKMAP (x86-32 only). Stub required because
arch/um/include/asm/fixmap.h includes it unconditionally.

--- /dev/null
+++ b/arch/arm64/um/asm/archparam.h
@@ -0,0 +1,5 @@
+/* SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0 */
+/* arm64 stub - LAST_PKMAP is x86-32 only */
+#ifndef __UM_ARCHPARAM_ARM64_H
+#define __UM_ARCHPARAM_ARM64_H
+#endif
